/*
    31--------26-25------21 ----------------------------------------0
    |  = COP1   |   fmt   |                                         |
    ------6----------5-----------------------------------------------
    |--000--|--001--|--010--|--011--|--100--|--101--|--110--|--111--| lo
 00 | MFC1  | DMFC1 | CFC1  | ---   | MTC1  | DMTC1 | CTC1  | ---   |
 01 | *1    | ---   | ---   | ---   | ---   | ---   | ---   | ---   |
